%N A394237 Number of circular parking functions of length n avoiding the pattern 122.
%H A394237 Lara Pudwell, <a href="https://faculty.valpo.edu/lpudwell/slides/AMS2025.pdf">Pattern avoidance in cyclic parking functions</a>, 2025.
%H A394237 Lara Pudwell, <a href="https://faculty.valpo.edu/lpudwell/papers/circpf.pdf">Pattern Avoidance in Circular Parking Functions</a>, Valparaiso Univ. (2026). See p. 6 (Table 2).
%F A394237 a(n) = 1 + Sum_{k=1..n-1} (binomial(n-1, k)^2*k!/(n - k)).
%F A394237 a(n) = A350267(n-1) + 1 for n>0. - _Hugo Pfoertner_, Mar 14 2026
%e A394237 For n=4, the a(4)=19 parking functions are 1111, 1112, 1113, 1114, 1123, 1124, 1132, 1134, 1142, 1143, 1213, 1214, 1234, 1243, 1314, 1324, 1342, 1423, 1432.
%p A394237 a := n -> local k; 1 + add(binomial(n - 1, k)^2*k!/(n - k), k = 1 .. n - 1):
%p A394237 seq(a(i), i = 0 .. 22);
%t A394237 Table[1 + Sum[(Binomial[n - 1, k]^2*k!/(n - k)), {k, n - 1}], {n, 0, 22}] (* _Michael De Vlieger_, Mar 13 2026 *)
